nameList.add("Stacey");
nameList.add("Bob");
nameList.add("Susan");
nameList.add("Pete");

for (int i = 0; i < nameList.size(); i++)
{
 /* missing code */
}

After the code segment is executed,  nameList  should contain  ["Bob", "Pete"].
